Regorafenib plus best supportive care versus placebo plus best supportive care 
in Asian patients with previously treated metastatic colorectal cancer (CONCUR): 
a randomised, double-blind, placebo-controlled, phase 3 trial.

Li J(1), Qin S(2), Xu R(3), Yau TC(4), Ma B(5), Pan H(6), Xu J(7), Bai Y(8), Chi 
Y(9), Wang L(10), Yeh KH(11), Bi F(12), Cheng Y(13), Le AT(14), Lin JK(15), Liu 
