How to routinely collect data on patient-reported outcome and experience 
measures in renal registries in Europe: an expert consensus meeting.

Breckenridge K(1), Bekker HL(2), Gibbons E(3), van der Veer SN(4), Abbott D(5), 
Briançon S(6), Cullen R(1), Garneata L(7), Jager KJ(8), Lønning K(9), Metcalfe 
W(10), Morton RL(11), Murtagh FE(12), Prutz K(13), Robertson S(14), Rychlik 
I(15), Schon S(16), Sharp L(17), Speyer E(18), Tentori F(19), Caskey FJ(20).

Author information:
(1)UK Renal Registry, Southmead Hospital, Bristol, UK.
(2)Leeds Institute of Health Sciences, School of Medicine, University of Leeds, 
